<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="better-n">better <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'betə(r)/    美 /'betər/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[可用单数] 较好的事物：</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="for-better-or-for-worse">for better or (for) worse</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不论好坏；不管是福是祸</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="for-the-better">for the better</h3>
<p>1.<strong>有所好转</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="so-much-the-better-worse">so much the better / worse</h3>
<p>1.<strong>这样更好 / 差：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If they can do them both at the same time, then so much the better. 
如果他们可以同时做这两件事，那当然更好。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The result is not very important to us, but if we do win, then so much <strong><em>_</em></strong>_better.  （2012 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. the  </p></div>